ms-vscode-remote.remote-wsl/query-expfea.comment: Logs queries to the experiment service by feature for metric calculations

ms-vscode-remote.remote-wsl/resolver.comment: Reports the use and outcome of a resolver

wslversion.comment: The WSL version installed of the selected ditro

connectionmethod.comment: The connection method used to connect to the server: 'localhost', 'wslExeProxy' or 'wsl2VMAddress'

failurereason.comment: In a case of failure, the reason: 'servererror', 'serverclose', 'timeout', 'wslnotfound', 'wslupdaterequired', 'undefined'

ms-vscode-remote.remote-wsl/welcomePage.comment: Tracks how the welcome page is used

outcome.comment: Interactions triggered from the welcome page: 'command' | 'link' | 'hide'

ms-vscode-remote.remote-wsl/openInWSL.comment: Tracks the use of the open command

origin.comment: From where the command was trggered. Currently only 'other'

iswslinstalled.comment: Whether WSL is installed on the OS

outcome.comment: What the user did with the notification: 'open' | 'hide' | 'show' | 'close'
What the user did with the dialog: 'open' | 'install' | 'show' | 'close'
